name: Hinata Hyūga (Pre-Shippuden)
description:
Hinata Hyuga from Naruto, her pre-Shippuden version

Use hinata_hyuuga to summon her, use short hair, blue hair, blunt bangs, sidelocks, white eyes, no pupils to form her head, use hoodie, forehead protector, jacket to summon her default attire...which may inaccurate.

Use L-WORD to make her looks younger, closer to an anime.

Recommended weight: 0.6-0.8
